  "elementalSkill": {
    "name": "Countermeasure: Lumi's Battle Cry!",
    "description": "Adventure with Lumi! Depending on how you Tap, Lumi attacks in different forms.\\n\\n<span style=\"color: #FFD780FF;\">Tap</span>\\nLumi strikes in a <span style=\"color: #FFD780FF;\"><button data-link=\"11300001\">Super Power Form</button></span>, attacking nearby enemies continuously, dealing <span style=\"color: #FFE699FF;\">AoE Geo DMG</span>. If there are Moondrifts nearby, Lumi will also deal <span style=\"color: #FFE699FF;\">AoE Geo DMG</span> to nearby enemies, which will be considered Lunar-Crystallize Reaction DMG.\\n\\n<span style=\"color: #FFD780FF;\">Continuous Tapping</span>\\nTime to show what we're really capable of! After using her Elemental Skill, Linnea will feed Lumi sparkling gemstones when her Elemental Skill or Normal Attack is Tapped repeatedly. A full-bellied Lumi will strike in her <span style=\"color: #FFD780FF;\"><button data-link=\"11300001\">Ultimate Power Form</button></span>, dealing an especially powerful instance of <span style=\"color: #FFE699FF;\">AoE Geo DMG</span> that is considered Lunar-Crystallize Reaction DMG, switching to <span style=\"color: #FFD780FF;\"><button data-link=\"11300001\">Standard Power Form</button></span>.\\nAdditionally, tapping the Elemental Skill increases Linnea's interruption resistance.\\n\\n<i>\"You're up, Lumi!\"</i>",
    "skillLabels": [
      "Lumi Pound-Pound Pummeler DMG",
